This paper is primarily focused on video analytics, which falls under the computer vision (cs.CV) sub-category. The paper also discusses the use of microclassifiers and edge computing, which are relevant to machine learning (cs.MM) and machine learning applications (cs.LG). The paper also discusses the need to process large volumes of data, which could fall under the distributed, parallel, and cluster computing (cs.DC) sub-category. Finally, the paper discusses the strain on network infrastructure, which could fall under the networking and internet architecture (cs.NI) sub-category.
